---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Docs | NetOps OS">
  <Header />
  <main class="page">
    <p class="label">Documentation</p>
    <h1>Documentation</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Documentation will be published as the project evolves, including installation notes, architecture decisions, development logs, and technical guides.
    </p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card"><h3>Getting Started</h3><p>Initial setup and project overview will be added soon.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Architecture Notes</h3><p>Design decisions and system structure will be documented here.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Development Logs</h3><p>Progress updates and milestones will be published regularly.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Use Cases</h3><p>Real-world network operations scenarios will be explained.</p></article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</MainLayout>
